(window.webpackJsonp=window.webpackJsonp||[]).push([[412],{1039:function(r,n){r.exports='\x3c!-- \r\ntitle: 02-HTML进阶\r\nsort: \r\n--\x3e \r\n# HTML进阶\r\n\r\n### 头\r\n\r\n- `<base>`\r\n\r\n  > `<base href="http://www.runoob.com/images/" target="_blank">`\r\n  >\r\n  > 作为所有链接标签的默认链接。\r\n\r\n- `<meta>`\r\n\r\n  > 元数据\r\n  >\r\n  > 为网页定义描述内容:\r\n  >\r\n  > `<meta name="description" content="fzf about html">`\r\n  >\r\n  > 设置自动刷新:\r\n  >\r\n  > `<meta http-eqiv="refresh" content="30"> `\r\n\r\n- `<link>`\r\n\r\n  > ```html\r\n  > <head>\r\n  > <link rel="shortcut icon" href="url">\r\n  > <title>这是一个带图片的标签</title>\r\n  > </head>\r\n  > ```\r\n\r\n### 图像\r\n\r\n`<img src="url" alt="image" border="2">`\r\n\r\n- `src`\r\n\r\n  > 图像源属性\r\n\r\n- `alt`\r\n\r\n  > 可替换的文本\r\n\r\n- `height/width`\r\n\r\n- `border`\r\n\r\n  > 设置边框粗细\r\n\r\n- `align`\r\n\r\n  > 设置图像对其\r\n\r\n### 表格\r\n\r\n- `<table>`\r\n\r\n  > 使用`border`设置边框\r\n  >\r\n  > `width height`设置长宽\r\n  >\r\n  > `# HTML5 不推荐`\r\n  >\r\n  > - `bgcolor`属性 - 可以设置背景颜色。\r\n  > - `background`属性 - 可以设置背景图像。\r\n  > - `bordercolor`属性 - 可以设置边框颜色。\r\n  >\r\n  > `cellspacing` - 定义单元格间距离\r\n  >\r\n  > `cellpadding` - 表示单元格边框与单元格内容之间的距离\r\n\r\n- `<th>`\r\n\r\n  > 定义标题\r\n  >\r\n  > `tr`定义行\r\n  >\r\n  > `td`定义元素\r\n  >\r\n  > `colspan` - 此单元格占多少行\r\n  >\r\n  > `rowspan` - 此单元格占多少列\r\n\r\n- `theader`\r\n\r\n  ```html\r\n  <table border = "1" width = "100%">\r\n      <thead>\r\n          <tr>\r\n              <td colspan = "4">This is the head of the table</td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n      </thead>\r\n           \r\n      <tfoot>\r\n          <tr>\r\n              <td colspan = "4">This is the foot of the table</td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n      </tfoot>\r\n           \r\n      <tbody>\r\n          <tr>\r\n              <td>Cell 1</td>\r\n              <td>Cell 2</td>\r\n              <td>Cell 3</td>\r\n              <td>Cell 4</td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n      </tbody>         \r\n  </table>\r\n  ```\r\n\r\n  | This is the head of the table |        |        |        |\r\n  | ----------------------------- | ------ | ------ | ------ |\r\n  | Cell 1                        | Cell 2 | Cell 3 | Cell 4 |\r\n  | This is the foot of the table |        |        |        |\r\n\r\n- 实践\r\n\r\n  ```html\r\n  <table border="2" cellpadding = "5">\r\n      <tr>\r\n          <th colspan="3">Our Classmates</th>\r\n      </tr>\r\n      <tr>\r\n          <td>fzf</td>\r\n          <td>🚹</td>\r\n          <td>18</td>\r\n      </tr>\r\n      <tr>\r\n          <td rowspan="2">ly</td>\r\n          <td>🚺</td>\r\n          <td>16</td>\r\n      </tr>\r\n      <tr>\r\n          <td>🚹</td>\r\n          <td>17</td>\r\n      </tr>\r\n  </table>\r\n  ```\r\n\r\n### 列表\r\n\r\n- 有序列表\r\n\r\n  > `ul`\r\n  >\r\n  > `li`\r\n\r\n- 无序列表\r\n\r\n  > `ol`\r\n\r\n- 自定义列表\r\n\r\n  ```html\r\n   <dl>\r\n   <dt>Coffee</dt>\r\n   <dd>- black hot drink</dd>\r\n   <dt>Milk</dt>\r\n   <dd>- white cold drink</dd>\r\n   </dl> \r\n  ```\r\n\r\n### 区块\r\n\r\n- `<div>`\r\n\r\n  > 分区块\r\n\r\n- `<span>`\r\n\r\n  > 组合行内元素\r\n\r\n  ```html\r\n  <p>我的母亲有 <span style="color:blue;font-weight:bold">蓝色</span> 的眼睛，我得父亲有 <span style="color:darkolivegreen;font-weight:bold">碧绿色</span> 的眼睛。</p>\r\n  \r\n  ```\r\n\r\n  ### 表单\r\n\r\n  ```html\r\n  <form name="input" action="html_form_action.php" method="get">\r\n  First name: <input type="text" name="firstname"><br>\r\n  Pass world: <input type="password" name="passwd"><br>\r\n  \r\n  <input type="radio" name="sex" value="male">Male<br>\r\n  <input type="radio" name="sex" value="female">Female<br>\r\n  \r\n  <input type="checkbox" name="vehicle" value="Bike">I have a bike<br>\r\n  <input type="checkbox" name="vehicle" value="Car">I have a car<br> \r\n  \r\n  <input type="text" placeholder="this is placeholder text">\r\n  <input type="submit" value="Submit">\r\n  \r\n  </form>\r\n  \r\n  ```\r\n\r\n### 框架\r\n\r\n> `<iframe src="URL"></iframe>`\r\n>\r\n> 在一个页面内插入另一个界面\r\n\r\n- 属性\r\n\r\n  > `frameborder="0"`\r\n  >\r\n  > 移除边框\r\n\r\n- 边距\r\n\r\n  > `padding`：内边距\r\n  >\r\n  > `margin`：外边距\r\n\r\n### 脚本\r\n\r\n- `<noscript>`：浏览器不支持脚本时使用\r\n\r\n### 字符实体\r\n\r\n> `&nbsp;` 空格\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n'}}]);